Sentencas: Fully stabilized zirconia (8YSZ) has been considered a promising candidate for fabricating electrolytes of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) due to the excellent oxygen ionic conductivity.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Recently, structural optimization of a fully stabilized zirconia (8YSZ) electrolyte via vat photopolymerization (VP) technology has shown great potential in improving performance.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Generally, preferable mechanical strength is required along with conductivity for the electrolyte structure.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: However, investigation on the mechanical properties of printed 8YSZ parts has been absent.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Herein, an optimized 8YSZ photosensitive slurry was developed and the overall performance of the printed parts was tested systematically.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The slurry with a high solid loading (50 vol %) exhibited a low viscosity (1.2 Pa center dot s, shear rate of 30 1/s).
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The printed parts showed superior mechanical (fracture toughness of 3.31 +/- 0.38 MPa center dot m0.5, flexural strength of 372 +/- 11 MPa) and electrochemical (ion conductivity of 4.03 x 10-2 S/cm at 800 degrees C) properties.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Besides, the characteristic size of the prepared complex three-dimensional (3D) electrolyte structure was as small as 100 mu m. Results indicated that the electrolytes achieved both comparable mechanical and electrochemical properties to those of conventional processes.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Therefore, VP technologies open up an avenue for the fabrication of robust and geometrically hyperfine 8YSZ electrolytes with good electrochemical performance.
Titulo: 3D Printing of Robust 8YSZ Electrolytes with a Hyperfine Structure for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
